OL,3,CBody found in search for missing
OL,4,Cformer police officer
OL,6,FPolice searching for a former officer
OL,7,Fwho had been missing for nearly three
OL,8,Fweeks have found a body.
OL,10,FJane Hiles, 52, was last seen at her
OL,11,Fhome in Apperley Bridge, West
OL,12,FYorkshire, on 24 February.
OL,14,FWest Yorkshire Police said underwater
OL,15,Fsearch teams recovered a body from the
OL,16,FRiver Aire near Kirkstall Abbey on
OL,17,FSunday.
OL,19,FFormal identification has not yet
OL,20,Ftaken place, but Ms Hiles' family has
OL,21,Fbeen informed.
