OL,3,CBody found in search for missing
OL,4,Cformer police officer
OL,6,FDet Insp Andy Queen, of Bradford CID,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Extensive enquiries have been
OL,8,Fongoing over the last few weeks to
OL,9,Ffind Jane and sadly officers have
OL,10,Ffound a body believed to be her.
OL,12,F"Specially trained officers are
OL,13,Fcontinuing to support her family at
OL,14,Fthis difficult time.
OL,16,F"We would like to thank the public who
OL,17,Fshared the appeal to find her."
OL,19,FMrs Hiles, a former police officer,
OL,20,Fworked as a dog groomer and regularly
OL,21,Fwalked in the Apperley Bridge area.
